#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: I was playing in the garden. Something happened!!"
msgstr "{F3_SON_7}: Saya sedang bermain di taman. Kemudian, sesuatu telah berlaku!!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_MOTHER}: What is it, {F3_SON_7}!? Take a breath and tell me."
msgstr "{F3_MOTHER}: Apa yang telah terjadi, {F3_SON_7}!? Tarik nafas dan beritahu Ibu."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{MAN_IN_CAR}: Hi boy. You have such a nice smile and lovely straight hair. What’s your name?"
msgstr "{MAN_IN_CAR}: Hai adik. Manisnya muka adik, rambut adik pun lurus dan cantik. Siapa nama adik?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: My name is {F3_SON_7}."
msgstr "{F3_SON_7}: Nama saya {F3_SON_7}."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{MAN_IN_CAR}: {F3_SON_7}, such a beautiful name."
msgstr "{MAN_IN_CAR}: {F3_SON_7}, sedapnya nama."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: Thank you."
msgstr "{F3_SON_7}: Terima kasih."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{MAN_IN_CAR}: {F3_SON_7}, I have chips and some toys for you in my car. If you come in, you can eat chips and play with all the toys, I promise…"
msgstr "{MAN_IN_CAR}: {F3_SON_7}, Jom ikut pakcik, pakcik ada jajan dan permainan dalam kereta pakcik. Kalau kamu ikut pakcik, kamu boleh makan jajan dan main semua permainan yang ada, pakcik janji…"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: No, thank you."
msgstr "{F3_SON_7}: Tidak, terima kasih."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: Mummyyyyyy!!"
msgstr "{F3_SON_7}: Ibu!!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_MOTHER}: {F3_SON_7}, I’m so proud of you for not getting out of our house gate and getting into the car. You remembered the rules we created about safety in this community. That was a dangerous situation. You are so brave. Thank you for telling me. I will report it so it doesn’t happen again."
msgstr "{F3_MOTHER}: {F3_SON_7}, Terima kasih kerana memanggil Ibu. Kamu sangat berani. Ibu bangga kerana kamu tidak keluar dari pagar rumah dan pergi ke kereta. Kamu ingat peraturan yang kita dah tetapkan tentang keselamatan dalam komuniti kita. Situasi ini sangat bahaya. Ibu akan buat laporan supaya perkara ini tidak terjadi lagi."

